  "content_id": "89e4b950-448d-41e3-b2ac-98e2d7a3cab6",
  "description": "How to store oil safely, check which oil storage regulations apply and pollution penalties",
  "details": {
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "hide_chapter_navigation": false,
